g the predictive maintenance scheduling based on the proposed\noptimization approach leads to an increased profit compared to the baseline\ndecision-making (perform maintenance at the degradation limit).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Apr 2021 07:01:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-15"}
