n for an LF, we also show that the proposed\npipeline also benefits light field view extrapolation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Apr 2021 12:03:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Apr 2021 02:38:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-29"}
